Restructured file/code: Renamed controller DiagnosticsController -> MonitorController. Split counter data access into separate actions. Renamed view monitor -> performance.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2422 | andlov | 2016-06-06 00:44:54 +0200 (Mon, 06 Jun 2016) | 1 line

Implemented sub counter mode. In this mode, performance data is viewed for a specific sub counter (e.g. server/cpu) across all servers having collected performance data.
