r2110 | andlov | 2015-03-13 11:32:39 +0100 (Fri, 13 Mar 2015) | 1 line

Adding exceptionAction() in GUI controller. Set exception handler in base class. Forward exception to GUI controller from dispatcher for sub system dependent error handling. All exceptions except 'not found' in GUI-layer is now logged to the system log.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2109 | andlov | 2015-03-13 04:32:38 +0100 (Fri, 13 Mar 2015) | 1 line

Unified error and exception handling in all controllers. Triggered errors and thrown exceptions in dispatcher, controller initialize and actions are reported back to client in a sub system dependent format (e.g. thru error page or by SOAP fault).
------------------------------------------------------------------------
r2108 | andlov | 2015-03-13 01:53:38 +0100 (Fri, 13 Mar 2015) | 1 line

