r1720 | andlov | 2014-10-02 04:18:03 +0200 (Thu, 02 Oct 2014) | 1 line

Aliases in hasMany() and belongsTo() should be in lower case. Then e.g. ->collection or ->getCollection() works with lazy loading and framework provided magic methods. See http://forum.phalconphp.com/discussion/545/many-to-many-relation.
